WEBVTT

00:02.335 --> 00:04.086
NOAH:
<i>I did not rape her!</i>

00:04.170 --> 00:05.755
{\an3}But you and Valerie
did have sex.

00:05.839 --> 00:07.215
I told you that.

00:07.298 --> 00:09.634
{\an1}She didn't say no or try
to resist in any way?

00:09.718 --> 00:12.137
{\an3}I told you
I did not rape her!

00:12.220 --> 00:13.847
You were drunk that night.

00:13.930 --> 00:16.433
Believe me, she was
as much into it as I was.

00:16.516 --> 00:18.059
That's not what she said.
She's lying.

00:18.143 --> 00:20.311
Is she lying about the
Rohypnol found in her blood?

00:20.395 --> 00:21.563
I don't know.

00:21.646 --> 00:22.939
The club was full of guys.

00:23.022 --> 00:23.982
It could've been anyone.

00:24.065 --> 00:26.401
{\an3}Yeah? But she had
sex with you.

00:28.361 --> 00:31.239
He's not denying
we had sex, is he?

00:31.322 --> 00:33.241
{\an1}He's saying
it was consensual.

00:33.324 --> 00:34.451
Pig.

00:34.534 --> 00:36.244
Do you have a sexual
history with him?

00:36.327 --> 00:37.579
What has that got
to do with anything?

00:37.662 --> 00:39.831
Valentine's Day,
old time's sake.

00:39.914 --> 00:41.666
What, and a roofie cocktail
to break the ice?

00:41.750 --> 00:42.917
I don't think so.

00:43.001 --> 00:44.169
Did he break up with you?

00:44.252 --> 00:45.253
Yeah, then he raped me.

00:45.336 --> 00:46.254
Go figure.

00:46.337 --> 00:47.422
If he raped you...

00:47.505 --> 00:48.631
Which he did.

00:48.715 --> 00:50.467
I want him prosecuted.

00:50.550 --> 00:52.135
And I'm sorry.

00:52.218 --> 00:54.179
But to do that, I need to know
that you didn't want it.

00:54.262 --> 00:55.138
Don't you get it?

00:55.221 --> 00:58.016
He took away my ability
to know what I wanted.

00:58.099 --> 01:00.185
I shouldn't be the
one on trial here.

01:00.268 --> 01:02.479
No, you shouldn't.

01:02.562 --> 01:05.565
But with date rape,
the victims usually are.

01:08.359 --> 01:10.487
What is taking so long?

01:10.570 --> 01:13.364
{\an1}It's rape, Donna,
it's a serious crime.

01:13.448 --> 01:14.157
David, he didn't rape her.

01:14.240 --> 01:15.658
He didn't even
sleep with her.

01:15.742 --> 01:17.660
{\an1}Yeah, they spent the night
together last night.

01:17.744 --> 01:20.413
{\an1}All right?
Open your eyes.

01:20.497 --> 01:22.499
I can't deal with this.

01:23.416 --> 01:25.960
Hey, are those pain
killers not working?

01:26.044 --> 01:27.754
Well, my back feels okay,

01:27.837 --> 01:30.507
but the pills sure
are wiping me out.

01:30.590 --> 01:33.176
I'm trying to hold off.

01:33.259 --> 01:37.013
Listen, I tore up my knee
skiing recently, you know?

01:37.096 --> 01:40.433
The pain was so bad, I just
started downing the pills.

01:40.517 --> 01:42.519
{\an3}I never knew being a zombie
could feel so good.

01:42.602 --> 01:43.520
I want the pain to go away,

01:43.603 --> 01:45.730
{\an1}but I want to be able
to function, too, you know?

01:45.814 --> 01:47.857
Yeah, that's why you
need one set of pills

01:47.941 --> 01:50.193
to counteract the other.
Is that what you did?

01:50.276 --> 01:53.822
Couple of D amphetamines,
and, uh, you'll be fine.

01:53.905 --> 01:55.365
When all this nonsense is over,

01:55.448 --> 01:57.450
I'll set you up, okay?

01:59.118 --> 02:01.830
{\an1}I just can't believe
what she's accusing him of.

02:01.913 --> 02:03.373
(sighs)

02:05.416 --> 02:07.669
Hey, you all right?

02:07.752 --> 02:09.253
Yeah. I just...

02:09.336 --> 02:10.713
I just want to go home.

02:10.797 --> 02:11.881
Um, what about Noah?

02:11.965 --> 02:13.341
{\an3}They're gonna
charge him, right?

02:13.424 --> 02:15.385
{\an1}No, not till tomorrow
after they talk to the D.A.

02:15.468 --> 02:17.595
I did not rape you!

02:17.679 --> 02:20.390
{\an3}Whoa, hey, hey, hey.
Hey, shut up, all right?!

02:20.473 --> 02:22.433
{\an3}Don't talk to her,
don't even look at her.

02:23.810 --> 02:27.397
How can you stand by him?

02:27.480 --> 02:28.731
Forget about them, okay?

02:28.815 --> 02:29.899
How'd it go in there?

02:29.983 --> 02:32.026
{\an1}I don't know,
it's her word against mine.

02:32.110 --> 02:34.529
{\an3}Look, we know you didn't
do anything, okay?

02:36.447 --> 02:37.615
Just give us a minute?

02:37.699 --> 02:39.742
Yeah, no problem.

02:42.495 --> 02:44.414
{\an3}I shouldn't drink
when I'm angry.

02:44.497 --> 02:45.748
Bad things happen.

02:45.832 --> 02:47.417
Don't blame yourself.

02:47.500 --> 02:49.711
You did nothing wrong here.

02:49.794 --> 02:52.380
Listen to me.

02:52.463 --> 02:55.049
Valerie and I,

02:55.133 --> 02:56.509
we did have sex.

02:58.845 --> 03:00.179
What?

03:00.263 --> 03:02.432
Look, I was drunk and jealous
about you and David.

03:02.515 --> 03:05.476
This isn't happening.

03:05.560 --> 03:07.979
I did not rape her.

03:08.062 --> 03:11.274
Tell me this isn't happening.

03:11.357 --> 03:14.068
I'm sorry.

03:30.376 --> 03:32.462
♪ ♪

03:59.739 --> 04:01.908
♪ ♪

04:25.932 --> 04:29.352
♪ I wanna take you to the top ♪

04:29.435 --> 04:32.021
♪ Yeah, nothing, baby ♪

04:32.105 --> 04:34.482
♪ Is gonna stop us now ♪

04:34.565 --> 04:36.025
♪ ♪

04:42.949 --> 04:45.368
♪<i> Whoo! Yeah!</i> ♪

04:45.451 --> 04:46.953
♪<i> Come on</i> ♪

04:47.036 --> 04:51.249
